 WebAuthn (Passwordless Auth)

Today's Focus: Biometric authentication.
What I Learned:

WebAuthn API

Public key credentials

Security keys

Code:

javascript
navigator.credentials.create({
    publicKey: {
        challenge: new Uint8Array([/* random bytes */]),
        rp: { name: "My Site" },
        user: { id: new Uint8Array([/* user id */]), name: "user@example.com" }
    }
});
